Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the winter\Nto spring transition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,La. La. La. laaaa. Oh, I\Nknow. I love it so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it its own\Nterm: Springsition!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha !
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to\Nre-label all my binders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after we finish--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Everything! We still\Nhave so much to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bustles and\Nbows! Rarity, did we--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Already hemmed, ruched\Nand cuffed, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:01:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, no reason to panic,\Nbut um, we seem to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,temporarily low. And when\NI say "temporarily low",
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean completely out of--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--The baby blue sapphires?\NThey arrived this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What\Nabout the design for the--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,--And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've really outdone\Nyourself this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Morning Sunshine\NTulip frock is gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. Now, I know\Nyou're worried about something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,slipping between the cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but with your managerial skills\Nand my fabulous designs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we have everything covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, you're right.\NThere are no cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be a dear and fetch\Nme some vermillion satin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll start on the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal Elegance Empire\Nsilhouette evening gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My most certain pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I love this picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time we had\Nthat kind of fun together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can't remember.\NHas it been that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've been so\Nbusy running my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Something, or\Nshould I say somepony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is slipping between\Nthe cracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss my Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, we're running\Nlow on vermillion satin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can order more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this is when we pretended\Nwe were storybook princesses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and here we pretended
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we were on a dangerous-\Nyet-stylish safari...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So many wonderful memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to put too fine a\Npoint on it but ....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle loves playing\Ndress up. I miss her so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't\Nyou go visit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could, but between\Nrunning three stores
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the springsition,\NI couldn't possibly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've already\Ndone almost all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, go! I have\Neverything well in hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Point taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to visit my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to immediately\Nturn that around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can spend the\Nwhole day together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can do all of\Nher favorite things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'd\Nlove that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sassy, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Now\Nget out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, sis. I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders\Nmid-mission, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun!\NLet's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoot, we've got\Na job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Chip Cutter.\NWe've done our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think I have\Nit in me to be a sculptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you said you\Nweren't good at anything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,except getting in trouble\Nfor making sculptures
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your lunch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't help it.\NWhen I look at my sandwich,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like it's just asking\Nme to turn it into a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is this slab asking\Nyou to turn it into?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmmm. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom: Wow!\NThat's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks\Njust like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew you had\Nit in you, Chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is way better than\Nsandwich sculpting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chip, we're proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got my cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad way\Nto start a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad way\Nat all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping ponies is just about\Nmy favorite thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Another satisfied client!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure it's Zipporwhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs help reconnecting\Nwith her cutie mark:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,three puppy paw prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When is she swinging by?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think she should be\Narriving right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, Zipporwhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so what seems to\Nbe the problem exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my puppy, Ripley.\NWe used to be so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I got my cutie\Nmark the day I found him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and took him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, it's like he wants\Nnothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry; you've\Ncome to the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cutie Mark Crusaders\Nare on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust us, before\Nyou know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you and your puppy will\Nbe back to being besties!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the CMC guarantee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we promise you'll have\Nour full attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who's here to\Nspend the whole day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with her little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry, dear! You're tiny.\NI didn't even see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tend to get carried\Naway with my entrances!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Ta da! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, what are\Nyou doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to spend\Nthe day with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited, I could\Npractically faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't happen to have a\Nfainting couch in here, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!\NIt's a tree house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be\Ntrès gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, well, I sure am happy to\Nsee you! And spending the day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with you does sound like\Na lot of fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda right in the middle\Nof something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have responsibilities and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Sweetie Belle.\NWe've got this covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How often do you get to\Nspend time with your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you two can\Nhandle our client here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Client?" Oh, that\Nis so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks? I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! You have mints to\Noffer your 'clients'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'professional'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you\Ntwo got this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have it handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Look at this\Nwall of satisfied customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls really\Nhave come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me know if you need\Nme or run into any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on. You'll never\Nguess what I have planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeal] So fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just I know how much\Nyou love these puppet shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just like old times!\NYou, me, greasy popcorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,... it's like no time\Nhas passed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Ooh! It's\Nyour favorite part!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Banana peels are so\Nvery, very slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny because\Nit's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I um, guess I just prefer black\Nbox experimental theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It's no\Nbig deal. This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Ta-da! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you excited to\Nbe back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I know my baby sister,\Nor do I know my baby sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah. Where\Nis "here," exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Stop being so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this is your\Nfavorite ice cream shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. From when\NI was a little filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I convinced the original\Nowner to come out of retirement
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you your all-time\Nfavorite dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I remember it\Nbeing much bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, go ahead. I know\Nyou're dying to dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... uh...\None tasty bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Still a little hungry though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get another sundae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate with rainbow\Nsprinkles perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking something\Nmore like a salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A salad? When did\Nyou get so practical?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um. I guess another\Nscoop would be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One more filly clown\Nsurprise, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ripley!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you must\Nbe bored, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very long line for\None of Twisty Pop's balloons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But just be patient; we'll\Nget you your favorite
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,balloon bouquet and\Nit'll all be worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a good puppy? Who's a good\Npuppy? You're the good puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come on, puppy-wuppy.\NGet the bally-wally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ripley!\NLike this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, Scootaloo! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if the ball\Ntasted better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nthat's it, Scoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like\Nit's going so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna do a quick\Ncheck with the CMC's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess duty calls\Nand you have that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, nothing, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Sweetie Belle, how's\Nyour day with Rarity going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not exactly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, it's like Rarity\Ndoesn't even know me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we could say our\Nday is going better--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--but we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Zipporwhill's puppy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't want anything\Nto do with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya know, it's an\Nawfully big puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle! Hurry;\Nhe's making it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know just what\Nto do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Love the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Love it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, you did "hate the\Ncamera" for all these shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon Zipporwhill,\Nyou can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, this is hard for\Nme to say, but... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been acting\Nweird all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to love doing\Nthese things with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it! I used to!\NThat's not who I am anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't who I am. My cutie\Nmark must be for something else
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because my puppy just\Ndoesn't love me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is you. You love\Npuppet shows and dressing up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and taking silly photos and tiny\Nlittle clown-shaped ice creams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! If you still think\NI like doing this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe you don't\Nknow me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Sweetie Belle\Ntalked to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And after everything I\Ndid to set up a whole day of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,doing her favorite things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, accusing me\Nof not knowing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know her better than anypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twisty, but the\Nhard truth is my sister
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is being unappreciative\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to go and give\Nher a piece of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zipporwhill. What\Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Apple\NBloom and Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're with my puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to like them\Nbetter than me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. He doesn't like doing\Nanything with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even want\Nto play with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And all puppies love these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that might be your\Nproblem right there. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Find Zipporwhill, Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof woof. Zipporwhill woof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zipporwhill! We're sorry we\Nhaven't figured this out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, girls; I\Nthink I cracked this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is! Oh, dear.\NReally should have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter. I'm going to give\Nher quite the talking to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after she's done\Nwith her conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger is no excuse for\Npoor manners, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Zipporwhill,\Nwhat do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I see.\NI see a full grown dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He did get bigger, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not just bigger,\Nhe's older too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't still play\Nwith the same toys
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from when you were\Na foal, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Ohhh! This squeaker is\Na little small for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just hard for me to\Nbelieve he's not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,adorable little guy\NI found anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. But doing\Nthings like you used to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,won't turn him\Nback into a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat him like the dog he is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and find new favorite\Nthings to do together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sweetie Belle. I heard what\Nyou said and you are so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,About the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but about us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I know you're\Nnot a little filly anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just the\Nlast time we did
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,all of those things together,\NI... I didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it was going to be\Nthe last, last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved doing those\Nthings with you;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard for me to\Nlet that go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Rarity. I love being with\Nyou too. That will never change!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe we could just try to\Ndo different things together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, puppy?\NI mean, Ripley?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, I\Nam so very proud
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of the pony\Nyou've grown into.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm proud that\Nno matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be\Nyour little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I uhh, have a little bit of time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,before I have to\Nhead to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we spend it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a grown pony\Nlike you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have one idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize your idea\Nwould be such a delicious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I'm\Ngoing to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll help you!
